---
title: Fajita-Inspired Beyond Meat® Flatbreads with Creamy Dressing and Cheddar Cheese
description: We're reimagining family-favourite fajitas as a no-fuss flatbread meal! Quick-cooking Beyond Meat® and peppers are seasoned with Tex-Mex paste and nestled atop toasted flatbreads, then finished with gooey cheddar cheese and a drizzle of creamy dressing.

